  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps 10 guests</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Le Lodge is a cosy, traditional duplex apartment-chalet above a quiet restaurant in the heart of the old village of Villeneuve, superbly convenient for your host’s night off!</p>
<p>The wooden cladding of the chalet gives it a true home-from-home ski lodge atmosphere, with rugs and comfy sofas in the open-plan lounge/dining area. The bedrooms all have private bath/shower and it is an ideal choice for a small group or family.</p>
<p>The superb location, in the centre of Villeneuve and a 5 minute walk from the nearest lift, the Télécabine d'Aravet, makes Chalet Le Lodge an ideal base for easy access to the sunny and extensive ski area of Serre Chevalier and the bars and restaurants in the evening.</p>
<p>Free ski and boot storage at the foot of the slopes in our partner equipment shop is also available.</p>]]></description>
